looping_key2: Agar aap game ko chala kar dekhoge, toh game sirf ek baar user se `input` leta hai. Aapko `code` `loop` mei daalna hai jisse ki user multiple baar letter daal daal kar try kar sake.
looping_key3: Aapko bahut jyada dhyaan rakhna hai, ki kaunsi instructions `loop` mei jayengi, kaunsi nahi?
looping_key5: Wohi instructions `loop` mei jayengi jo aapko lagta hai ki aapko repeat karni hai - e.g.
looping_key6: user se `input` aapko har baar lena hai, toh woh `loop` mei jana chahiye
looping_key7: Jab hum print karte hai "welcome to the game", woh sirf ek baar karein toh theek hai, toh isliye woh `loop` mei nahi hona chahiye
looping_key11: Aapka solution alag ho sakta hai, depending on ki aap `loop` mei kaise enter karte hai, aur kaise `loop` se exit karte hai.
